title: 20 - A Mind Set Free
description:
We don’t simply wait for our minds to change, we train. Day in, day out. On our knees. With Bibles open. This season has been an incredible journey together and we want to remember some of our favorite moments.

Download the DWELL App: https://dwellapp.io/jennie

Find Get Out of Your Head book: http://getoutofyourheadbook.com

Download the FREE Get Out of Your Head book club kit: http://jennieallen.com

Join us live at http://ifgathering.com/tv every Wednesday at 7 PM CT starting April 1st.
